<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="insist-v">insist <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'sɪst/    美 /ɪn'sɪst/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>坚持；坚决要求</strong></h4>
<p>to demand that sth should happen：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Why don't you call them up today?
为什么不今天就给他们电话呢？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— OK, <strong>if you insist</strong>. 
好，如果一定要我这样办的话。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>insist on / upon (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I insist on an immediate answer.
我坚决要求立即答复。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tu Youyou and her team members even insisted on testing the medicine on themselves to make sure that it was safe.
屠呦呦和她的队友们甚至坚持在自己身上试验这种药，以确保它是安全的。</p><footer>人教新选必① – 1</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>insist + (that) … (should) do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He insisted (that) the problem (should) be discussed at the meeting.
他执意要求在会上讨论这个问题。</p><footer>2010 湖北改</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>坚持说；坚持认为</strong></h4>
<p>to say firmly that sth is true, especially when others don’t believe you：</p>
<ul>
<li>insist on sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He insisted on his innocence. 
他坚持说自己是无辜的。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>insist + (that) 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He insisted that he was right. 
他坚持认为自己是对的。</p></div>

<p>注: insist表示“坚持”和“坚决要求”时，that从句中用虚拟语气；而表示“坚持说”和“坚持认为”时则不用。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The man insisted on<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (find) a taxi for me even though I told him I lived nearby.
  （2004 江苏改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. finding  </p></div>